lead_paragraph: Auburn and LSU played the last weekend of September and both coaches were under pressure. The ugly game had a bizarre ending. The next day LSU fired coach Les Miles, while Auburn and Gus Malzahn were feeling fortunate to be 2-2.

headline.print_headline: AP COLLEGE FOOTBALL PICKS: LSU, Auburn Back in Contention
